          </div>
          <p class="comment-text">This piece nails something I've been trying to articulate for months. The "two-tier content economy" framing is exactly right. What worries me most is that the collapse of the middle means fewer entry-level opportunities for writers to develop. How do you build the chops to write at the top tier if the apprenticeship rungs are being removed?</p>
