              <p class="reply-text">Marcus — this is exactly the question I kept circling back to while writing this piece. My honest answer: I don't know yet. But I suspect the apprenticeship model will shift toward working alongside AI systems rather than just producing content independently. What that looks like in practice is still being invented.</p>
